+frameInbox('Raison d\'etre')
	div
		ul
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='1') Game development is a world of many heroes, a few stars and a very few superstars
			li.fragment(data-fragment-index='3') Yet, it's still a magnificent world that outlines a path upon which you can leave your own footprints
		.text-center.mt-20.fragment(data-fragment-index='1')
			img.height-600(src=imgAssets+'kingdom_come.jpg')